tely,users in countries which are in the early stages of ICT development encounter higher cost of access as companies have to factor in capital costs as well as a lower user", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "0fe42b0a-d259-4df0-be44-f54e3b2738df": {"__data__": {"id_": "0fe42b0a-d259-4df0-be44-f54e3b2738df", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-2005-promoting-ict-human-development-asia-summary", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Asia-Pacific Human Development 2005: Promoting ICT for Human Development in Asia - Summary", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-2005-promoting-ict-human-development-asia-summary", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "3138bb2f8f332d0b93bebb8d8c294742203e0c142fd757c0df5540b7dc9ced0c"}, "3": {"node_id": "76d274bc-c377-437c-bc5d-d0b099cc02b0", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-2005-promoting-ict-human-development-asia-summary", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "81facc8dc46f414f1df0e2411898d657309c7dcce51d11592b0255729b88d363"}}, "hash": "1f6bb578dace6e601f41ffbf62f254643b3032e16dc3c98e83a36c8e0bce21f0", "text": "base.Data on internet retail pric- ing reveals enormous usage cost differences across countries (Figure 6.1 & Table 6.3). While the average usage costs o