otori, Ruangrai Tokrisna, Lam Quoc Tuan, Tereso S. Tullao, Nguyen Viet Vinh and Swarnim Wagl\u00e9. Technical Consultations The Report also draws on feedback and opinions expressed in regional technical consultations where inputs were obtained from experts within Acknowledgements and outside UNDP. Participants were Rashmi Banga, Anuradha Bhasin, Elena Borsatti, Javed Burki, Jolita Butkeviciene, Rupa Chanda, C.P. Chandrasekhar, Kay Kirby Dorji, Ramesh Gampat, Jayati Ghosh, Murray Gibbs, Cherie Hart, Cristina Hernandez, Susan Howes, Achila Imchen, T. Indrani, Mumtaz", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "fc2019c1-f02b-4061-b6c6-8fce69f31ce1": {"__data__": {"id_": "fc2019c1-f02b-4061-b6c6-8fce69f31ce1", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-report-2006-trade-human-terms", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Asia-Pacific Human Development Report 2006: Trade on Human Terms", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-report-2006-trade-human-terms", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "7991abca54482342d392f40bcb5c3ab3230588ce8765a8631900823751fd3828"}, "3": {"node_id": "41e88150-cc9f-427a-9e67-9cdd02c25826", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/asia-pacific-human-development-report-2006-trade-human-terms", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash